hints.content: When we skip count by hundreds,  we add $100$ to each number as we count.

Jada started with $476$,  so we need to add $100$ more to $476$.

$476 + 100 =576$

The next number Jada will say is $576$.

Jada is still skip counting by hundreds so we need to add $100$ to $576$.

$576+ 100 =676$

The next number Jada will say is $676$.
